  <Summary>A Vision of Death: Dr. Battu returns to the lab after a forced vacation only to learn that his Creech experiment has been modified and weaponized. The Creech is now a genetically enhanced fighting monster cloned from the DNA of an aborted fetus and alien genetic material. Outraged by the perversion of his work, Dr. Battu brings a news reporter in to the AGENCY labs to show him what they are doing there. He gives him a vial of alien DNA as proof of his claims. Battu then utilizes a machine to transfer his consciousness into the Creech. Dross interrupts the process and shoots him in the head.

</Summary>
